-- Yuan to Appreciate in `Long Run,' Former Hong Kong Central Banker Yam Says
-- Sophie Leung
-- 2010-07-02T01:21:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/yuan-to-appreciate-in-long-run-former-hong-kong-central-banker-yam-says.html

          
          
             Former Hong Kong Monetary Authority
Chief Executive Joseph Yam said the Chinese yuan will appreciate
“in the long run.” He spoke today in a radio interview in Hong
Kong.  
